Abolished 1.4.1966 and divided between the parishes of Gloucester, 
    Hucclecote and Upton St. Leonards. See also Table 2, notes (a) and (l).

Renamed 3.7.1956 to become the parish of Brookthorpe with Whaddon. 
    See also Table 2, notes (a) and (f).

Created 3.7.1956 by renaming the parish of Brookthorpe. See also 
    Table 2, note (o).

Abolished 1.4.1966 and divided between the parishes of Gloucester, 
    Highnam and Minsterworth. See also Table 2, notes (a) and (l).

Created 14.9.1967 by renaming the parish of Longlevens. See also 
    Table 2, note (o).

Renamed 14.9.1967 to become the parish of Innsworth. See also 
    Table 2, notes (a) and (l).

Renamed 1.4.1974 to become the parish of Staunton Coleford. See 
    also Table 2, notes (b), (i) and (o).

Renamed 9.11.1945 to become the parish of Whitminster. See also 
    Table 2, note (f).

Created 9.11.1945 by renaming the parish of Wheatenhurst. See 
    also Table 2, note (o).

Abolished 1.4.1951 and added to the parish of Gloucester. 
    See also Table 2, note (a).
